{"word":"χρήστης","slug":"χρήστης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χρήστης</b></el> <el>(χρήστης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>χρήστων</el> (not <el>χρηστῶν</el>, to distinguish it from the <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> of <el>χρηστός.</el>)\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>χράω3</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a creditor, usurer, dun</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(from the <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>) <i>a debtor</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}